COMPOSER REQUIRE
-------------

composer require wikimedia/composer-merge-plugin


ADD TO EXISTING SECTION "EXTRA"
---------------

"merge-plugin": {
    "include": [
        "web/modules/contrib/ckeditor_codemirror/composer.libraries.json"
    ]
},

UPDATE LOCK FILE & INSTALL
-------------

composer update --lock

composer install


INSTALL MODULE
-------------

composer require ckeditor-plugin/ckeditor_codemirror
